loginStep0Explanation: Ngenisa idilesi yemeyile yakho ukuze uqalise.
loginStep1Explanation: Faka igama eliyimfihlo ukuze ungene kwiakhawunti yakho.
step3Subtitle: Ubuncinane bamagama asi-8, unobumba om-1, inani eli-1
signupStep0Explanation: Ngenisa idilesi yemeyile ukwenza iakhawunti yakho. Unokusebenzisa ukungena kuGoogle ukufikelela ngokukhawuleza.
signupStep1Explanation: Khetha igama lakho lokubonisa. Le yindlela abanye abasebenzisi abaza kukubona ngayo kwiChat.
signupStep2Explanation: Igama lakho lomsebenzisi liqala nge @ isimboli. Esi sichongi sahlukileyo sinceda abanye ukuba bakufumane. Akekho omnye umsebenzisi onokuba nethegi efanayo.
signupStep3Explanation: Yenza igama eliyimfihlo elinamandla ukukhusela iakhawunti yakho.
signupStep4Explanation: Qinisekisa igama eliyimfihlo kwaye wamkele imigaqo yokubhalisa.
